# Unshared files
Assets/images/SF3/
Assets/images/SVC/

Assets/sounds/SF3/
Assets/sounds/SVC/

# Videos — recordings and pose-visualization output.
# NOTE: Visualized_Data/*.mp4 and output_pose_video.mp4 are already tracked
# from earlier commits; this rule only stops NEW videos being added.
*.mp4

# Model weights (.pth) and label encoders (.pkl) ARE tracked — they're small
# (KB to ~1MB) and the repo has versioned them since early on. Don't add a
# blanket ignore for them; datasets and videos are the size problem, not these.

# Images are tracked: game sprites in Assets/images/, the README thumbnail,
# and model classification reports. No blanket *.png ignore here on purpose.

# Claude Code project config (local only)
.claude/

# Pose datasets — raw, labeled, split and augmented. Kept out of git; shared
# out-of-band instead. NOTE: ~1735 .csv files are already tracked from earlier
# commits, so this rule only stops NEW data being added.
*.csv